title: POWER WALK // 10 Minute Taylor Swift Treadmill Walking Workout • Low Impact HIIT Cardio
description:
This 10 minute treadmill workout is a TAYLOR SWIFT walking workout for a low impact HIIT cardio burn! Featuring STYLE, ...READY FOR IT? and WILDEST DREAMS. This treadmill workout is great for beginners! 
I'm so happy you're here to power walk through the next 10 mins with me! Let's goooooo!

If you're here on a menopause weight loss journey, watch this!! https://youtu.be/sEEX11IGQkY

Who needs Peloton workout videos when you have YouTube!? Click LIKE and SUBSCRIBE to help support my channel! 
Thank you!

FULL TREADMILL WALKING WORKOUT:
2 Minute Warm-Up
3 x 2 Minute Power Walking Sets
*Set Rest: 1 Minute Brisk Walk
